     C* DEBUG basic test. H-spec col 15 = '1' enables DEBUG. Turns on
     C* indicator 05, sets VALFLD=123, then DEBUG dumps both to DBGOUT.
     H        1
     FDBGOUT  O   F    80              DISK
     C                     SETON                     05
     C                     Z-ADD123       VALFLD
     C           'LBL1'    DEBUGDBGOUT    VALFLD
